de.hu_berlin.german.korpling.saltnpepper.misc.treetagger

Interface Token

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotatableElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TokenImpl

    public interface Token
extends AnnotatableElement
    A representation of the model object 'Token'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Text
    • Pos Annotation
    • Lemma Annotation
    • Document
    • Spans

    See Also:
    TreetaggerPackage.getToken()
